Subject: [eVuln] miniBloggie Authentication Bypass


New eVuln Advisory:
miniBloggie Authentication Bypass
http://evuln.com/vulns/47/summary.html

--------------------Summary----------------
Vendor: myWebland
Vendor's Web Site: http://mywebland.neopages.net/
Software: miniBloggie
Versions: 1.0
Critical Level: Moderate
Type: SQL Injection
Class: Remote
Status: Unpatched
Exploit: Available
Solution: Not Available
Discovered by: Aliaksandr Hartsuyeu (eVuln.com)
eVuln ID: EV0047

-----------------Description---------------
Vulnerable scripts:
login.php

Username and password isn't properly sanitized before being used in a SQL query. This can be used to log in as administrator without password.

Condition: gpc_magic_quotes: off

--------------Exploit----------------------
Available at: http://evuln.com/vulns/47/exploit.html


--------------Solution---------------------
No Patch available.

